            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-Hd1e108">Rubrica 3</head>
            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-Hd1e111" type="question-title">De conscientia benignitatis et malignitatis</head>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-d1e114">
               <lb ed="#V" n="61"/>¶ De conscientia benignitatis
      <lb ed="#V" n="62"/>et malignitatis. ¶ Rubrica. 3
    </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-d1e121">
               <lb ed="#V" n="63"/> <ref>ORatius epistolarum li.
      <lb ed="#V" n="64"/>i. e. i.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-Qd1e127">Hic murus
      <lb ed="#V" n="65"/>eneus extat: Nil conscii sibi: nul
      <lb ed="#V" n="66" break="no"/>la pallescere culpa.</quote> 
    </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-d1e134">
               <lb ed="#V" n="67"/>
                <ref>¶ Tullius de senectute:</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-Qd1e138">Conscientia bene acte
        <lb ed="#V" n="68"/>vite multorumque beneficiorum recordatio ino
        <lb ed="#V" n="69"/>cundissima est.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-d1e147"> <ref>/ Idem tuscalanarum que
        <lb ed="#V" n="70"/>stionum li. 2.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-Qd1e149">Nullum theatrum virtute et
        <lb ed="#V" n="71"/>conscientia maius est.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-d1e157">
               <lb ed="#V" n="72"/>
                <ref>¶ Quidius de fastis li. i.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-Qd1e161">Conscientia mens
        <lb ed="#V" n="73"/>vt cuique sua est sic concipit intra Pectore
        <lb ed="#V" n="74"/>profecto spemque metumque suo.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-d1e169"> <ref>/ Lib. 4</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-Qd1e171">Con
        <lb ed="#V" n="75" break="no"/>scia mens recti fame mendacia ridet.
        <lb ed="#V" n="76"/>Sed nos in vitium credula turba sumus.</quote>
        <lb ed="#V" n="77"/> <ref>¶ Seneca in prouerb.</ref> <quote>Plerique famam: conscien
        <lb ed="#V" n="78"/>tiam pauci verentur.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-d1e183">
               <lb ed="#V" n="79"/>
                <ref>¶ Paulus apostolus epistola. 2. ad corinth. c. i.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-Qd1e187">Slia
        <lb ed="#V" n="80"/>nostra hoc est testimonium conscient ie nostre.</quote>
        <lb ed="#V" n="81"/><ref>¶ Statius thebandos li. 2.</ref> <quote>O sper timidum scelus</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-d1e195">
               <lb ed="#V" n="82"/>
                <ref>¶ Iuuenalis li. 2. satis i.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-Qd1e199">Cui frigida mens est
        <lb ed="#V" n="83"/> Criminibus tacita sudant praecordia culpa.</quote>
        <lb ed="#V" n="84"/> <ref>¶ Marcialis cocus li. vndique suscepto. c. 6.</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="85"/> <quote>Ibis ad occultos tramites loca deuia mundi
        <lb ed="#V" n="86"/>Peccatum tecum est: conscientie culpa comes.
        <lb ed="#V" n="87"/>Alterius censor: censor et esto tuus. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-d1e213">
               <lb ed="#V" n="88"/>
                <ref>¶ Ambrosius de officiis li. 2. c. i.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-Qd1e217">Uitam bea
        <lb ed="#V" n="89"/>tam effciunt tranquillitas conscientie et se
        <lb ed="#V" n="90" break="no"/>curitas innocentie. <!--79.xml-->
        <pb ed="#V" n="26-v"/>
                  <cb ed="#V" n="a"/>
               </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-d1e232">
               <lb ed="#V" n="1"/>
                <ref>¶ Augustinus in epig. prospe. 8. emp.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-Qd1e236">Bo
        <lb ed="#V" n="2" break="no"/>na conscientia tranquillum facit animu.</quote>
        <lb ed="#V" n="3"/> <ref>Macrobius de somno scipionis li. 2. et fi.</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="4" /> <quote>Uirtutis fructum sapiens in conscientia ponit:
        <lb ed="#V" n="5"/>minus perfctus in gloria. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-d1e248">
               <lb ed="#V" n="6"/>
                <ref>¶ Cato. c. 2.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-Qd1e252">Conscius ipse sibi: de se putat
        <lb ed="#V" n="7"/>omnia dici. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-d1e258">
               <lb ed="#V" n="8"/>
                <ref>¶ Cassiodorus epistolarum li. 7. c. 32.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-Qd1e262">Totum vi
        <lb ed="#V" n="9"/>tiosum geritur vbi conscientie puritas non ha
        <lb ed="#V" n="10"/>betur.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-d1e270"> <ref>/ Li. 8. e. 18.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-Qd1e272">Sicut conscientia leta est
        <lb ed="#V" n="11"/>que prouehitur meritis: ita sub reatu iacet
        <lb ed="#V" n="12"/>qui se imparem cognoscit muneribus conse
        <lb ed="#V" n="13" break="no"/>cutis.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-d1e282"> <ref>/ Libro. 11. c. 8.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-Qd1e284">Quid acquiri puta
        <lb ed="#V" n="14" break="no"/>tur vbi conscientia bona perditur.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-d1e290">
               <lb ed="#V" n="15"/>
                <ref>¶ Isidorus soliloquiorum li. 2. c. 3.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-Qd1e294">Deus con
        <lb ed="#V" n="16" break="no"/>scientias iudicat.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-d1e301"> <ref>/ c. 37.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-Qd1e303">Etsi non te damnet
        <lb ed="#V" n="17"/>publica fama: condennat propria conscia.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-d1e309"> <ref>/ c. 38</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="18"/> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-Qd1e311"> Conscientia rei semper tin pena est. Mens
        <lb ed="#V" n="19"/>male conscientie propriis agitatur stimulis. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-d1e319">
               <lb ed="#V" n="20"/>
                <ref>¶ Prouerb. vulgar.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d19731-Qd1e323">Lamore guasta la conscia </quote>
            </p>
         </div>
